                    <span>there are so many facts here. I haven't read them all, but there seem to be a lot more than in the last edition. they are really a lot that opens your eyes to hugeness of the world in which we all humans live.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">a good compilation but historically inaccurate at critical</div>
